work.summary:
Management of data team defining team structure, roles and development path for each one.
Contributed to the definition of data and tech architecture, looking at performance, costs and priorities considering the main company goals.
Achievements:
- Migration of a big legacy data integration architecture to Airflow in order to reduce costs;
- Improvement of team performance with study sessions, coaching and management;
- Add monitoring and code quality checks and quick bug solutions in order to keep company key data available and reliable for all the areas;
- Mentoring of other squads to define tech solutions and how they can interact better with data team.

Contributed with the team development and coaching while dealing with technical solutions together with business, product and design squad members in order to deliver great products. 
Some of our achievements:
- Improvement of the React Native app with the best development practices, CI/CD, tests, modularity, observability and so on;
- Development of the backend squad knowledge in the event based architecture on AWS tooling to work with backend structure in order to achieve feature developments;
- Geospacial Favo Entrepreneurs Search, an architecture to find the closest entrepreneur for each client given a set of criterias (Reduced time to respond web and app clients and improved user experience);
- Development and improvement of relationships between tech and product teams, seeking for best practices and agile practices in order to improve the company productivity.
